 value#1</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"tooltip__arrow\" data-popper-arrow></div></div></div></div></header><ol class=\"meanings meanings--search-result\"><li class=\"meanings__meaning\" data-cy=\"lemma-meaning\">people value (it/them) so for him/her, people price (it/them) so for him/her\n                    <cite class=\"cite-dict\" data-has-tooltip aria-describedby=\"tooltip:120\">🤖CW </cite><div id=\"tooltip:120\" class=\"tooltip\" role=\"tooltip\" data-cy=\"citation-tooltip\">\n        \n            Experimental automatically inflected form of CW definition\n        \n        <div class=\"tooltip__arrow\" data-popper-arrow></div></div></li><li class=\"meanings__meaning\" data-cy=\"lemma-meaning\">people give him/her such a price on (it/them)\n                    <cite class=\"cite-dict\" data-has-tooltip aria-describedby=\"tooltip:121\">🤖CW </cite><div id=\"tooltip:121\" class=\"tooltip\" role=\"tooltip\" data-cy=\"citation-tooltip\">\n        \n            Experimental automatically inflected form of CW definition\n        \n        <div class=\"tooltip__arrow\" data-popper-arrow></div></div></li><li class=\"meanings__meaning\" data-cy=\"lemma-meaning\">people give him/her at a set price.\n                    <cite class=\"cite-dict\" data-has-tooltip aria-describedby=\"tooltip:122\">🤖MD </cite><div id=\"tooltip:122\" class=\"tooltip\" role=\"tooltip\" data-cy=\"citation-tooltip\">\n        \n            Experimental automatically inflected form of MD definition\n        \n        <div class=\"tooltip__arrow\" data-popper-arrow></div></div></li><li class=\"meanings__meaning\" data-cy=\"lemma-meaning\">It is priced at so much for him.\n                    <cite class=\"cite-dict\" data-has-tooltip aria-describedby=\"tooltip:123\">MD </cite><div id=\"tooltip:123\" class=\"tooltip\" role=\"tooltip\" data-cy=\"citation-tooltip\"><span class=\"source-title\">Maskwacîs Dictionary</span>.\n          Maskwacîs, Maskwachees Cultural College, 1998.\n        \n        <